title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race Season 8 - Episode 8
description:
Bob and Monét review Drag Race Season 8 Episode 8 as the queens prep paper-thin looks for a "Book Ball" and pay homage to "Strangers with Candy" icon Jerii Blank.
See Monét and Bob on tour this summer by going to bobandmonet.com !!
